A `SelectPanel` is used when the user needs to select one or more items from a list. It combines a trigger button with a dropdown panel containing searchable, selectable items. The ability to search for items is what mainly separates this from the `ActionMenu` in our usage.

## With footer button

When selections need to be explicitly confirmed before taking effect, add a footer with an action button (ideally "Apply"). This pattern is used in workflow settings for role selection.

